rite.</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2Faxulart.itch.io%2Fsmall-8-direction-characters" class="post_action reply_btn" data-register_action="community_reply">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div data-post="{&quot;user_id&quot;:10683812,&quot;id&quot;:15474778}" class="community_post has_vote_column" id="post-15474778"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2Faxulart.itch.io%2Fsmall-8-direction-characters" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn" title="Vote up" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg width="20" role="img" class="svgicon icon_vote_up" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" version="1.1" height="20"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2Faxulart.itch.io%2Fsmall-8-direction-characters" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn" title="Vote down" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg width="20" role="img" class="svgicon icon_vote_down" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" version="1.1" height="20"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/shaluka"><div style="background-image: url(https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzI1NDg1MTYzLnBuZw==/25x25%23/vCmWSP.png)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/shaluka">Shaluka</a></span><span title="2026-02-14 08:21:58" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/15474778">115 days ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"></span></div><div class="post_content"><div class="post_body user_formatted" dir="auto"><p>Thanks a lot am using your sprites to&nbsp;learn isometric movement ,, :)</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2Faxulart.itch.io%2Fsmall-8-direction-characters" class="post_action reply_btn" data-r