<p>I did some recoloring, I understand that with your CC-BY license I could post the recolorings (palette swap) along with other sprites I draw in case someone wants to use them? Do you want me to send them to you instead?</p>
</div><div class="post_footer"><a href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2Faxulart.itch.io%2Fsmall-8-direction-characters" class="post_action reply_btn" data-register_action="community_reply">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div class="community_post_replies top_level_replies"><div data-post="{&quot;user_id&quot;:4038971,&quot;id&quot;:13140153}" class="community_post has_vote_column is_reply" id="post-13140153"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2Faxulart.itch.io%2Fsmall-8-direction-characters" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn" title="Vote up" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg width="20" role="img" class="svgicon icon_vote_up" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" version="1.1" height="20"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2Faxulart.itch.io%2Fsmall-8-direction-characters" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn" title="Vote down" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg width="20" role="img" class="svgicon icon_vote_down" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" version="1.1" height="20"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/axulart"><div style="background-image: url(https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzE2ODg4Nzc3LnBuZw==/25x25%23/heZgc%2B.png)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/axulart">AxulArt</a></span><span title="2025-06-15 18:03:15" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/13140153">358 days ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"><span class="upvotes">(+2)</span></span></div><div class="post_content"><div class="post_body user_formatted" dir="auto"><p>Hi, sorry for taking so long to reply!. I&#x27;m fine with it, don&#x27;t worry; it&#x27;s enough for me if the credits say, &quot;Modified or based on AxulArt&#x27;s sprites.&quot; I&#x27;m glad they were helpful (I&#x27;ve actually pretty much have forgotten itch.io, so I should consider uploading new art assets soon).</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2Faxulart.itch.io%2Fsmall-8-direction-characters" class="post_action reply_btn" data-register_action="community_reply">Reply</a></div></div></div></div></div><div data-post="{&quot;user_id&quot;:3129881,&quot;id&quot;:10735104}" class="community_post has_replies has_vote_column" id="post-10735104"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2Faxulart.itch.io%2Fsmall-8-direction-characters" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn" title="Vote up" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg width="20" role="img" class="svgicon icon_vote_up" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" version="1.1" height="20"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2Faxulart.itch.io%2Fsmall-8-direction-characters" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn" title="Vote down" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg width="20" role="img" class="svgicon icon_vote_down" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" version="1.1" height="20"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/gamedevmix"><div style="background-image: url(https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzQwNjIyOTIucG5n/25x25%23/LVAwWR.png)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/gamedevmix">GameDevMix</a></span><span title="2024-08-25 11:30:28" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/10735104">1 year ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"></span></div><div class="post_content"><div class="post_body user_formatted" dir="auto"><p>What viewing/camera angle would you say these are drawn at, please? Trying to improve my understanding!</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2Faxulart.itch.io%2Fsmall-8-direction-characters" class="post_action reply_btn" data-register_action="community_reply">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div class="community_post_replies top_level_replies"><div data-post="{&quot;user_id&quot;:4038971,&quot;id&quot;:10817344}" class="community_post has_vote_column is_reply" id="post-10817344"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2Faxulart.itch.io%2Fsmall-8-direction-characters" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn" title="Vote up" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg width="20" role="img" class="svgicon icon_vote_up" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" version="1.1" height="20"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2Faxulart.itch.io%2Fsmall-8-direction-characters" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn" title="Vote down" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg width="20" role="img" class="svgicon icon_vote_down" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" version="1.1" height="20"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/axulart"><div style="background-image: url(https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzE2ODg4Nzc3LnBuZw==/25x25%23/heZgc%2B.png)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/axulart">AxulArt</a></span><span title="2024-09-04 19:58:46" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/10817344">1 year ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"><span class="upvotes">(+1)</span></span></div><div class="post_content"><div class="post_body user_formatted" dir="auto"><p>I made it thinking about a topdown game, but it also works for isometric view.</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2Faxulart.itch.io%2Fsmall-8-direction-characters" class="post_action reply_btn" data-register_action="community_reply">Reply</a></div></div></div></div></div><div data-post="{&quot;user_id&quot;:11035220,&quot;id&quot;:10217690}" class="community_post has_vote_column" id="post-10217690"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2Faxulart.itch.io%2Fsmall-8-direction-characters" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn" title="Vote up" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg width="20" role="img" class="svgicon icon_vote_up" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" version="1.1" height="20"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2Faxulart.itch.io%2Fsmall-8-direction-characters" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn" title="Vote down" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg width="20" role="img" class="svgicon icon_vote_down" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" version="1.1" height="20"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/albersj66"><div style="background-image: url(/static/images/frog.png)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/albersj66">albersj66</a></span><span title="2024-06-30 15:20:18" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/10217690">1 year ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"><span class="upvotes">(+2)</span></span></div><div class="post_content"><div class="post_body user_formatted" dir="auto"><p>Thanks for the great asset pack! Used it in my personal game project (<a href="https://github.com/JosefAlbers/moulinet" referrerpolicy="origin" rel="nofollow noopener">https://github.com/JosefAlbers/moulinet</a>).</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2Faxulart.itch.io%2Fsmall-8-direction-characters" class="post_action reply_btn" data-register_action="community_reply">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div data-post="{&quot;user_id&quot;:9081253,&quot;id&quot;:9867555}" class="community_post has_replies has_vote_column" id="post-9867555"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2Faxulart.itch.io%2Fsmall-8-direction-characters" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn" title="Vote up" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg width="20" role="img" class="svgicon icon_vote_up" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" version="1.1" height="20"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2Faxulart.itch.io%2Fsmall-8-direction-characters" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn" title="Vote down" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg width="20" role="img" class="svgicon icon_vote_down" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" version="1.1" height="20"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/axolt-studio"><div style="background-image: url(https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzE0MzU4MTc1LnBuZw==/25x25%23/aaN16S.png)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/axolt-studio">Axolt Studio</a></span><span title="2024-05-07 04:56:43" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/9867555">2 years ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"></span></div><div class="post_content"><div class="post_body user_formatted" dir="auto"><p>Muchas gracias por estos recursos, son hermosos, demuestra que haces un gran trabajo, espero que tu vida vaya muy bien y alcances tus sueños.</p>
<p>(perdón si está escrito mal, el inglés no es mi idioma nativo)</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2Faxulart.itch.io%2Fsmall-8-direction-characters" class="post_action reply_btn" data-register_action="community_reply">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div class="community_post_replies top_level_replies"><div data-post="{&quot;user_id&quot;:4038971,&quot;id&quot;:9873277}" class="community_post has_vote_column is_reply" id="post-9873277"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2Faxulart.itch.io%2Fsmall-8-direction-characters" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn" title="Vote up" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg width="20" role="img" class="svgicon icon_vote_up" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" version="1.1" height="20"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2Faxulart.itch.io%2Fsmall-8-direction-characters" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn" title="Vote down" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg width="20" role="img" class="svgicon icon_vote_down" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" version="1.1" height="20"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/axulart"><div style="background-image: url(https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzE2ODg4Nzc3LnBuZw==/25x25%23/heZgc%2B.png)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/axulart">AxulArt</a></span><span title="2024-05-08 04:22:13" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/9873277">2 years ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"><span class="upvotes">(+1)</span></span></div><div class="post_content"><div class="post_body user_formatted" dir="auto"><p>Gracias, me alegra que te guste (quiero hacer lo posible por estar mas activo en itch.io pero por lo general tardo mucho en contestar los comentarios en esta plataforma). Por cierto,&nbsp;mi lenguaje principal es el español y la mayoría de mis clientes en fiverr hablan ingles; así que no veo ningún problema con el&nbsp;mensaje :D</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2Faxulart.itch.io%2Fsmall-8-direction-characters" class="post_action reply_btn" data-register_action="community_reply">Reply</a></div></div></div></div></div><div data-post="{&quot;user_id&quot;:10196206,&quot;id&quot;:9613075}" class="community_post has_replies has_vote_column" id="post-9613075"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2Faxulart.itch.io%2Fsmall-8-direction-characters" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn" title="Vote up" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg width="20" role="img" class="svgicon icon_vote_up" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" version="1.1" height="20"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2Faxulart.itch.io%2Fsmall-8-direction-characters" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn" title="Vote down" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg width="20" role="img" class="svgicon icon_vote_down" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" version="1.1" height="20"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/starrjacked"><div style="background-image: url(https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzE1MzYxNzkwLnBuZw==/25x25%23/Lb8%2BeT.png)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/starrjacked">StarrJacked</a></span><span title="2024-03-23 15:57:45" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/9613075">2 years ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"></span></div><div class="post_content"><div class="post_body user_formatted" dir="auto"><p>These are amazing!!! Could you create a layerable template? I tried making one myself, but I couldn&#x27;t differentiate between articles of clothing like I&#x27;m sure you could... If that&#x27;s too much effort, that&#x27;s fine, these are beautiful and I WILL make them work.&nbsp; Thank you so much for free quality!</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2Faxulart.itch.io%2Fsmall-8-direction-characters" class="post_action reply_btn" data-register_action="community_reply">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div class="community_post_replies top_level_replies"><div data-post="{&quot;user_id&quot;:4038971,&quot;id&quot;:9620036}" class="community_post has_vote_column is_reply" id="post-9620036"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2Faxulart.itch.io%2Fsmall-8-direction-characters" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn" title="Vote up" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg width="20" role="img" class="svgicon icon_vote_up" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" version="1.1" height="20"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2Faxulart.itch.io%2Fsmall-8-direction-characters" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn" title="Vote down" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg width="20" role="img" class="svgicon icon_vote_down" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" version="1.1" height="20"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/axulart"><div style="background-image: url(https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzE2ODg4Nzc3LnBuZw==/25x25%23/heZgc%2B.png)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/axulart">AxulArt</a></span><span title="2024-03-24 20:49:41" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/9620036">2 years ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"></span></div><div class="post_content"><div class="post_body user_formatted" dir="auto"><p>I&#x27;m glad you like them. I was planning to expand it in the future, but right now I&#x27;ve been very busy with so many Fiverr orders; so I can&#x27;t assure you anything right now...</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2Faxulart.itch.io%2Fsmall-8-direction-characters" class="post_action reply_btn" data-register_action="community_reply">Reply</a></div></div></div></div></div><div data-post="{&quot;user_id&quot;:5971340,&quot;id&quot;:9565879}" class="community_post has_replies has_vote_column" id="post-9565879"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2Faxulart.itch.io%2Fsmall-8-direction-characters" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn" title="Vote up" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg width="20" role="img" class="svgicon icon_vote_up" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" version="1.1" height="20"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2Faxulart.itch.io%2Fsmall-8-direction-characters" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn" title="Vote down" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg width="20" role="img" class="svgicon icon_vote_down" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" version="1.1" height="20"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/thaeux"><div style="background-image: url(/static/images/frog.png)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/thaeux">Thaeux</a></span><span title="2024-03-16 07:57:23" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/9565879">2 years ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"></span></div><div class="post_content"><div class="post_body user_formatted" dir="auto"><p>This asset fitted perfectly for my game. Thank you very much. ☺️</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2Faxulart.itch.io%2Fsmall-8-direction-characters" class="post_action reply_btn" data-register_action="community_reply">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div class="community_post_replies top_level_replies"><div data-post="{&quot;user_id&quot;:4038971,&quot;id&quot;:9571922}" class="community_post has_vote_column is_reply" id="post-9571922"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2Faxulart.itch.io%2Fsmall-8-direction-characters" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn" title="Vote up" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg width="20" role="img" class="svgicon icon_vote_up" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" version="1.1" height="20"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2Faxulart.itch.io%2Fsmall-8-direction-characters" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn" title="Vote down" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg width="20" role="img" class="svgicon icon_vote_down" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" version="1.1" height="20"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/axulart"><div style="background-image: url(https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzE2ODg4Nzc3LnBuZw==/25x25%23/heZgc%2B.png)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/axulart">AxulArt</a></span><span title="2024-03-17 01:01:14" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/9571922">2 years ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"></span></div><div class="post_content"><div class="post_body user_formatted" dir="auto"><p>You&#x27;re welcome! I have somewhat forgotten them, but I am glad that they are useful to you</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2Faxulart.itch.io%2Fsmall-8-direction-characters" class="post_action reply_btn" data-register_action="community_reply">Reply</a></div></div></div></div></div><div data-post="{&quot;user_id&quot;:7514426,&quot;id&quot;:8283151}" class="community_post has_replies has_vote_column" id="post-8283151"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2Faxulart.itch.io%2Fsmall-8-direction-characters" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn" title="Vote up" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg width="20" role="img" class="svgicon icon_vote_up" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" version="1.1" height="20"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2Faxulart.itch.io%2Fsmall-8-direction-characters" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn" title="Vote down" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg width="20" role="img" class="svgicon icon_vote_down" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" version="1.1" height="20"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/develoafer"><div style="background-image: url(https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzEyODg3NjUwLmpwZw==/25x25%23/OzJ22v.jpg)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/develoafer">Develoafer</a></span><span title="2023-07-25 00:37:33" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/8283151">2 years ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"><span class="upvotes">(+4)</span></span></div><div class="post_content"><div class="post_body user_formatted" dir="auto"><p>Apologies for my inability to detect simple differences haha, but is this 16x16, 8x8, or smth else? Great pack btw</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2Faxulart.itch.io%2Fsmall-8-direction-characters" class="post_action reply_btn" data-register_action="community_reply">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div class="community_post_replies top_level_replies"><div data-post="{&quot;user_id&quot;:4038971,&quot;id&quot;:8901286}" class="community_post has_vote_column is_reply" id="post-8901286"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2Faxulart.itch.io%2Fsmall-8-direction-characters" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn" title="Vote up" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg width="20" role="img" class="svgicon icon_vote_up" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" version="1.1" height="20"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2Faxulart.itch.io%2Fsmall-8-direction-characters" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn" title="Vote down" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg width="20" role="img" class="svgicon icon_vote_down" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" version="1.1" height="20"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/axulart"><div style="background-image: url(https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzE2ODg4Nzc3LnBuZw==/25x25%23/heZgc%2B.png)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/axulart">AxulArt</a></span><span title="2023-11-19 02:04:31" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/8901286">2 years ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"><span class="upvotes">(+3)</span><span class="downvotes">(-1)</span></span></div><div class="post_content"><div class="post_body user_formatted" dir="auto"><p>Hello, sorry for taking so long to respond to you (I think I&#x27;m just going to answer your question in case anyone else needs it).</p>
<p>To make it easier, interpret it as 16x24px in size (although in reality they are 16x17px in size, but it is easier to interpret it the other way).</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2Faxulart.itch.io%2Fsmall-8-direction-characters" class="post_action reply_btn" data-register_action="community_reply">Reply</a></div></div></div></div></div><div data-post="{&quot;user_id&quot;:7926886,&quot;id&quot;:7925035}" class="community_post has_replies has_vote_column" id="post-7925035"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2Faxulart.itch.io%2Fsmall-8-direction-characters" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn" title="Vote up" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg width="20" role="img" class="svgicon icon_vote_up" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" version="1.1" height="20"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2Faxulart.itch.io%2Fsmall-8-direction-characters" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn" title="Vote down" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg width="20" role="img" class="svgicon icon_vote_down" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" version="1.1" height="20"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/dustdfg"><div style="background-image: url(https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzEyMTM1MTUzLnBuZw==/25x25%23/CVocaM.png)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/dustdfg">dustdfg</a></span><span title="2023-06-07 09:29:50" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/7925035">3 years ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"><span class="upvotes">(+3)</span></span></div><div class="post_content"><div class="post_body user_formatted" dir="auto"><p></p><p>You should add the license into metadata for the asset pack(s):         </p>
<p>&quot;Edit  asset pack-&gt;Metadata-&gt;Release Info-&gt;License for                             assets&quot;       It will increase the size of  audience      that    will     be      able    to        find your art         
</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2Faxulart.itch.io%2Fsmall-8-direction-characters" class="post_action reply_btn" data-register_action="community_reply">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div class="community_post_replies top_level_replies"><div data-post="{&quot;user_id&quot;:5272826,&quot;id&quot;:8550497}" class="community_post has_vote_column is_reply" id="post-8550497"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2Faxulart.itch.io%2Fsmall-8-direction-characters" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn" title="Vote up" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg width="20" role="img" class="svgicon icon_vote_up" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" version="1.1" height="20"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2Faxulart.itch.io%2Fsmall-8-direction-characters" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn" title="Vote down" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg width="20" role="img" class="svgicon icon_vote_down" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" version="1.1" height="20"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/goreldeen"><div style="background-image: url(https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzE5NDQyOTQ1LnBuZw==/25x25%23/Xtk8zo.png)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/goreldeen">GorEldeen</a></span><span title="2023-09-07 15:37:12" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/8550497">2 years ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"><span class="upvotes">(+2)</span></span></div><div class="post_content"><div class="post_body user_formatted" dir="auto"><p>Thank you man for helping others &lt;3</p>
