ttps://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2Faxulart.itch.io%2Fsmall-8-direction-characters" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn" title="Vote up" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg width="20" role="img" class="svgicon icon_vote_up" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" version="1.1" height="20"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2Faxulart.itch.io%2Fsmall-8-direction-characters" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn" title="Vote down" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg width="20" role="img" class="svgicon icon_vote_down" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" version="1.1" height="20"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/teten"><div style="background-image: url(/static/images/frog.png)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/teten">teten</a></span><span title="2022-12-12 12:15:37" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/7016879">3 years ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"><span class="upvotes">(+1)</span></span></div><div class="post_content"><div class="post_body user_formatted" dir="auto"><p>thank you im using it as a reference for my blacksmith character</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2Faxulart.itch.io%2Fsmall-8-direction-characters" class="post_action reply_btn" data-register_action="community_reply">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div data-post="{&quot;user_id&quot;:1300920,&quot;id&quot;:6977208}" class="community_post has_vote_column" id="post-6977208"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2Faxulart.itch.io%2Fsmall-8-direction-characters" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn" title="Vote up" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg width="20" role="img" class="svgicon icon_vote_up" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" version="1.1" height="20"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2Faxulart.itch.io%2Fsmall-8-direction-characters" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn" title="Vote down" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg width="20" role="img" class="svgicon icon_vote_down" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" version="1.1" height="20"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/wanderinghobo"><div style="background-image: url(https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzQxMTYxOTMucG5n/25x25%23/TKv3uM.png)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/wanderinghobo">Matt Carr</a></span><span title="2022-12-03 10:01:46" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/6977208">3 years ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"><span class="upvotes">(+1)</span></span></div><div class="post_content"><div class="post_body user_formatted" dir="auto"><p>Super cute and the exact reference I needed for a new project</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2Faxulart.itch.io%2Fsmall-8-direction-characters" class="post_action reply_btn" data-register_action="community_reply">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div data-post="{&quot;user_id&quot;:4399163,&quot;id&quot;:6827601}" class="community_post has_vote_column" id="post-6827601"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2Faxulart.itch.io%2Fsmall-8-direction-characters" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn" title="Vote up" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg width="20" role="img" class="svgicon icon_vote_up" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" version="1.1" height="20"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2Faxulart.itch.io%2Fsmall-8-direction-characters" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn" title="Vote down" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg width="20" role="img" class="svgicon icon_vote_down" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" version="1.1" height="20"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/driftware"><div style="background-image: url(https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzkzMDIxNzkucG5n/25x25%23/hbXdg4.png)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/driftware">DriftWare</a></span><span title="2022-10-27 20:41:08" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/6827601">3 years ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"><span class="upvotes">(+1)</span></span></div><div class="post_content"><div class="post_body user_formatted" dir="auto"><p>very earthbound-esque. I like it!</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2Faxulart.itch.io%2Fsmall-8-direction-characters" class="post_action reply_btn" data-register_action="community_reply">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div data-post="{&quot;user_id&quot;:4038971,&quot;id&quot;:4607323}" class="community_post has_replies has_vote_column" id="post-4607323"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2Faxulart.itch.io%2Fsmall-8-direction-characters" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn" title="Vote up" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg width="20" role="img" class="svgicon icon_vote_up" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" version="1.1" height="20"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2Faxulart.itch.io%2Fsmall-8-direction-characters" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn" title="Vote down" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg width="20" role="img" class="svgicon icon_vote_down" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" version="1.1" height="20"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/axulart"><div style="background-image: url(https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzE2ODg4Nzc3LnBuZw==/25x25%23/heZgc%2B.png)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/axulart">AxulArt</a></span><span title="2021-09-23 22:44:00" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/4607323">4 years ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"><span class="upvotes">(+3)</span></span></div><div class="post_content"><div class="post_body user_formatted" dir="auto"><p><span lang="en"><span>Hi, if anyone has any ideas for a new asset I&#x27;d really appreciate it;</span> <span>because I run out of ideas very quickly;</span> <span>so I am currently free for suggestions to bring you new assets while practicing pixelart.</span></span></p></div><div class="post_footer"><a href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2Faxulart.itch.io%2Fsmall-8-direction-characters" class="post_action reply_btn" data-register_action="community_reply">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div class="community_post_replies top_level_replies"><div data-post="{&quot;user_id&quot;:634224,&quot;id&quot;:4729992}" class="community_post has_vote_column is_reply" id="post-4729992"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2Faxulart.itch.io%2Fsmall-8-direction-characters" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn" title="Vote up" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg width="20" role="img" class="svgicon icon_vote_up" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" version="1.1" height="20"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2Faxulart.itch.io%2Fsmall-8-direction-characters" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn" title="Vote down" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg width="20" role="img" class="svgicon icon_vote_down" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" version="1.1" height="20"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/arcalum"><div style="background-image: url(/static/images/frog-blue.png)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/arcalum">Arcalum</a></span><span title="2021-10-13 13:29:56" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/4729992">4 years ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"><span class="upvotes">(+2)</span></span></div><div class="post_content"><div class="post_body user_formatted" dir="auto"><p>You can expand on your characters with different clothing, hair, npcs types. A sheet file with layers separating hat, hair, clothing, etc. And expand the animations to basic use, tool/weapon swing, lie down/death, chair sitting. You can start having a Patreon or charging for future works  to collect support. You have a pretty solid base here, they&#x27;re really cute!</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2Faxulart.itch.io%2Fsmall-8-direction-characters" class="post_action reply_btn" data-register_action="community_reply">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div data-post="{&quot;user_id&quot;:634224,&quot;id&quot;:4746446}" class="community_post has_vote_column is_reply" id="post-4746446"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2Faxulart.itch.io%2Fsmall-8-direction-characters" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn" title="Vote up" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg width="20" role="img" class="svgicon icon_vote_up" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" version="1.1" height="20"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2Faxulart.itch.io%2Fsmall-8-direction-characters" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn" title="Vote down" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg width="20" role="img" class="svgicon icon_vote_down" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" version="1.1" height="20"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/arcalum"><div style="background-image: url(/static/images/frog-blue.png)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/arcalum">Arcalum</a></span><span title="2021-10-16 15:36:54" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/4746446">4 years ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"><span class="upvotes">(+6)</span></span></div><div class="post_content"><div class="post_body user_formatted" dir="auto"><p>I notice the hat blinking in the last 3 directions of the Red Cap Boy: SW, W, NW<img src="https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzcyMTU5OTAuZ2lm/original/hKP%2BnA.gif" loading="lazy"></p><p>I&#x27;ve included the the little fix in this uploaded image:<br></p><p><img src="https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzcyMTYwNTcucG5n/original/vEgyIA.png" loading="lazy"><br></p></div><div class="post_footer"><a href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2Faxulart.itch.io%2Fsmall-8-direction-characters" class="post_action reply_btn" data-register_action="community_reply">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div data-post="{&quot;user_id&quot;:6182045,&quot;id&quot;:6814491}" class="community_post has_vote_column is_reply" id="post-6814491"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2Faxulart.itch.io%2Fsmall-8-direction-characters" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn" title="Vote up" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg width="20" role="img" class="svgicon icon_vote_up" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" version="1.1" height="20"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2Faxulart.itch.io%2Fsmall-8-direction-characters" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn" title="Vote down" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg width="20" role="img" class="svgicon icon_vote_down" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" version="1.1" height="20"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/eggnaut"><div style="background-image: url(/static/images/frog.png)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/eggnaut">eggnaut</a></span><span title="2022-10-24 22:42:09" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/6814491">3 years ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"><span class="upvotes">(+2)</span><span class="downvotes">(-1)</span></span></div><div class="post_content"><div class="post_body user_formatted" dir="auto"><p>Military stuff?</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2Faxulart.itch.io%2Fsmall-8-direction-characters" class="post_action reply_btn" data-register_action="community_reply">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div data-post="{&quot;user_id&quot;:4399163,&quot;id&quot;:7055476}" class="community_post has_vote_column is_reply" id="post-7055476"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2Faxulart.itch.io%2Fsmall-8-direction-characters" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn" title="Vote up" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg width="20" role="img" class="svgicon icon_vote_up" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" version="1.1" height="20"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2Faxulart.itch.io%2Fsmall-8-direction-characters" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn" title="Vote down" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg width="20" role="img" class="svgicon icon_vote_down" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" version="1.1" height="20"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/driftware"><div style="background-image: url(https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzkzMDIxNzkucG5n/25x25%23/hbXdg4.png)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/driftware">DriftWare</a></span><span title="2022-12-20 18:15:59" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/7055476">3 years ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"><span class="upvotes">(+2)</span></span></div><div class="post_content"><div class="post_body user_formatted" dir="auto"><p>Well, when I actually cut these up to use in animation, the frames aren&#x27;t centered in the same way and the animation doesn&#x27;t look very good.</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2Faxulart.itch.io%2Fsmall-8-direction-characters" class="post_action reply_btn" data-register_action="community_reply">Reply</a></div></div></div></div></div><div data-post="{&quot;user_id&quot;:3636446,&quot;id&quot;:4552863}" class="community_post has_vote_column" id="post-4552863"><div id="last-post" class="post_anchor"></div><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2Faxulart.itch.io%2Fsmall-8-direction-characters" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn" title="Vote up" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg width="20" role="img" class="svgicon icon_vote_up" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" version="1.1" height="20"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2Faxulart.itch.io%2Fsmall-8-direction-characters" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn" title="Vote down" data-register_action="community_vote"><svg width="20" role="img" class="svgicon icon_vote_d